universum.studios.android.intent

Class MimeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.android.intent.MimeType

  • public abstract class MimeType
extends Object
    This class specifies the most commonly used MIME types for a content distributed on devices powered by the Android.

    Text based types:

    • TEXT
    • TEXT_PLAIN
    • TEXT_HTML

    Image based types:

    • IMAGE
    • IMAGE_JPEG
    • IMAGE_PNG
    • IMAGE_BITMAP

    Audio based types:

    • AUDIO
    • AUDIO_MP3
    • AUDIO_MP4
    • AUDIO_MPEG

    Video based types

    • VIDEO
    • VIDEO_MP4
    • VIDEO_MPEG
    • VIDEO_JPEG
    • VIDEO_3GP
    • VIDEO_3GP2
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
